        <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
        <p class="last-updated">Last Updated: January 15, 2026</p>

        <div class="highlight-box">
            <p><strong>TL;DR:</strong> CFD Penney is designed with privacy in mind. We don't collect personal data, don't track you, and don't sell your information. Your annotations and collaboration sessions are peer-to-peer and not stored on our servers.</p>
